name: Welcome to earth
description: #Part5 Hello humans, welcome to earth! After Beca banned Rupi and Zel from her realm they were (kinda) obligated to go back to earth. Hope these little ones had a good and safe trip. Well, now I can say that the next adventures on earth will be a special chapter on their lives. Hope you all stay safe humans, and enjoy this new chapter of some incredible adventures. Can you already guess what they're up to? A big meow to you all. P.S.: this was a collab with @eternagnose who made this lovely soundtrack! 🍄🌎🐈‍⬛
